NOTE 20  EMPLOYEE STOCK AND SAVINGS PLANS

WE GRANT STOCK-BASED COMPENSATION TO DIRECTORS AND EMPLOYEES. AT JUNE 30, 2012, AN AGGREGATE OF 507 MILLION SHARES

WERE AUTHORIZED FOR FUTURE GRANT UNDER OUR STOCK PLANS, COVERING STOCK OPTIONS, STOCK AWARDS, AND SHARED PERFORMANCE STOCK AWARDS, AND EXCLUDING SHARES RESERVED FOR ISSUANCE UNDER OUR EMPLOYEE STOCK PURCHASE PLAN. AWARDS THAT EXPIRE OR ARE CANCELED

WITHOUT DELIVERY OF SHARES GENERALLY BECOME AVAILABLE FOR ISSUANCE UNDER THE PLANS. WE ISSUE NEW SHARES OF MICROSOFT COMMON STOCK TO SATISFY EXERCISES AND VESTINGS OF AWARDS GRANTED UNDER ALL OF OUR STOCK PLANS.

